{
  "text": "A change in consciousness should result in a greater distortion toward service to others, toward unity with all, and toward knowing in order to serve. Is this correct? And are there any other desirable? These are commendable phrases. The heart of white magic is the experience of the joy of union with the Creator. This joy will of necessity radiate throughout the life experience of the positive abdict. It is for this reason that sexual magic is not restricted solely to the negatively oriented polarizing heads, but when most carefully used has its place in high magic as it when correctly pursued joins body, mind and spirit with the one infinite creator any purpose which you may frame. Should we suggest take into consideration this basic union with the One Infinite Creator, for this union will result in service to others of necessity.",
